Narcos19 Records releases the official music video for P-Ray‘s latest single “One Day“. Eyiwumi Olawale Pelumi (born February 22,) known as P-Ray, is a Nigerian singer and song writer. A native of Ilorin state. P ray as a lover of music grew interest in music at a very young age. This is his official single under Narcos19 Records. The visuals for ‘One Day‘ was shot at Ebutte meta axis of Lagos and was directed by Adams Gud for Adams Gud Motionz. Watch and Enjoy!   The post [Video] P-Ray – “One Day” appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: Too Xclusive